and you retreat, it could feel like this.

236
00:11:02,145 --> 00:11:04,586
In some cases, it made losing feel like victory.

237
00:11:05,106 --> 00:11:07,546
It's a strategic retreat where you don't fall victim

238
00:11:07,626 --> 00:11:08,706
to your opponent's gambit.

