00:47:34,146 --> 00:47:37,427
We were like, hey, just so you know, the cards don't pass through that ring.

1011
00:47:37,447 --> 00:47:39,007
They come from there out or whatever.

1012
00:47:39,227 --> 00:47:44,469
I wouldn't have known that personally, but they helped make sure that anybody who sees this game

1013
00:47:44,489 --> 00:47:49,490
who's a big Marvel fan says, oh yeah, that's exactly the right color of that character or whatever.

1014
00:47:51,511 --> 00:47:52,952
