00:48:19,419 --> 00:48:21,262
Well, yeah, that's on Marvel.

1032
00:48:21,302 --> 00:48:22,604
Marvel controls all the merch.

1033
00:48:22,724 --> 00:48:25,668
So I tweet at Marvel, I guess.

1034
00:48:25,808 --> 00:48:28,312
So the real question would be, how much time

1035
00:48:28,352 --> 00:48:30,995
was there between when you started brainstorming this

1036
00:48:31,436 --> 00:48:34,941
to talking to Marvel, like having something to show them,

1037
00:48:35,121 --> 00:48:36,443
and then actually getting contract?

1038
00:48:37,757 --> 00:48:44,099
So we, the guy who runs Marvel Games, Jay Ong, used to work with me and Hamilton a long ago.

