00:48:52,282 --> 00:48:57,024
But he knew that we had made great stuff in the past together, and he wanted to work with us again.

1042
00:48:57,384 --> 00:49:00,965
So we had the suspicion that we might get to work with Marvel, but...

1043
00:49:02,645 --> 00:49:05,086
It was probably on the order of months

1044
00:49:05,146 --> 00:49:06,427
before we showed them anything.

1045
00:49:06,927 --> 00:49:10,008
And I don't know how long the contract took,

1046
00:49:10,028 --> 00:49:12,268
but we were friends, so it kind of.

1047
00:49:12,609 --> 00:49:13,289
Thank you so much.

